sequenceDiagram
    participant G as Go Producer
    participant P as RocketMQ Proxy
    participant S as SendMessageProcessor
    participant D as DefaultMessageStore
    participant C as CommitLog/MappedFile
    participant H as Flush/HA

    G->>P: gRPC SendMessage
    P->>S: Remoting SEND_MESSAGE
    S->>S: 校验Topic、权限、大小、属性和队列
    S->>D: asyncPutMessage(msgInner)
    D->>C: asyncPutMessage
    C->>C: 编码并追加到MappedFile
    C->>H: 提交刷盘与复制请求
    H-->>C: PUT_OK或超时状态
    C-->>D: PutMessageResult
    D-->>S: PutMessageResult
    S-->>P: 响应码、MessageID、QueueOffset
    P-->>G: SendReceipt或RPC错误
